<!doctype html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>BOMOO</title>
        <meta name="layout" content="home">     
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="div960" style="height: 135px;">
            <asset:image class="logo" src="logo.png" alt="bomoo"/>
            <div class="banner">
                <h5> Bank Of Maharashtra Officers Organization </h5>
                <p> God Country Organization Family </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="div960">
            <div id="home-carousel" class="carousel slide"> 
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="item active"> <asset:image src="3.jpg" alt="babasahebAmbedkar"/> </div>
                    <div class="item"> <asset:image src="2.jpg" alt="tiranga"/> </div> 
                    <div class="item"> <asset:image src="4.jpg" alt="bramha"/> </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="div960" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <div id="about-us" style="height: 48px; width: 100%; background-color: #ddd;  padding-top: 1px;">
                <p style="font-size: 20px; margin-left: 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans'; margin-top: 10px;">BOMOO - Voice of People</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12" style="text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto; margin-top: 20px;">
                    <asset:image class="pull-right" src="registrationCertificate.jpg" alt="Registration Certificate" style="margin-left: 20px; border : 1px solid gray;" />
                    <p>It’s an organisation of the officers, for the officer and by the officers, founded on 21st December 1977 and get registered on 4th Aug 1978 under Trade Unions Act 1926. It is affiliated to National Organisation of Bank Officers (NOBO) and Bhartiya Mazdoor Sangh (BMS) the largest trade union in the country.</p>
                    <asset:image class="pull-left" src="balasahebFadanvis.jpg" alt="balasahebFadanvis" style="margin-right: 20px;" />
                    <p>Our ideology is Nation first, next Institution and lastly Individual. At present we have a strength 1400+ soldiers. We are proud to state that new generation officers have always been backbone of BOMOO. At present, 90 % young Officers are members of BOMOO and are contributing in the success of Bank as well as BOMOO.</p>
                    <p>The organisation firmly believes that the prosperity of the employees lies in the progress of the Bank. It is guiding the members to follow the principles of the great visionaries like Shri Balasaheb Fadanvis & Shri K. S. Bhide who have laid the strong foundations of the organisation. The next generation of leadership is marching on the same lines.</p>
                    <p>We pledge ourselves to be the watchdogs, whistle blowers and keen followers of the Ethical Banking culture which was some time back redefined by our then Chairman and Managing Director Shri A. S. Bhattacharya.</p>
                    <p>BOMOO achieved MAJORITY status in 1980 and has maintained it for the last 25 years. It is re-established on 9th April 2002, 31st Oct 2005 and March 2008. We do miss our departed leaders and we wish to pay homage to Late Ketkar ji, Shri Narayan ji, Shri Gurav ji, Shri D. K.Deshpande ji who always strived for the betterment of the organisation, sacrificed everything & worked selflessly for the cause of the employees.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;"/>
            <div style="background-color: #fff; text-align: left;">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4 ideology" >   
                        <div class="media" > 
                            <a class="pull-left" href="#">
                                <span class="fa fa-flag ideology-icon"></span>
                            </a> 
                            <div class="media-body" style="padding-left: 10px; padding-top: 5px;">
                                <p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Nation Above All</strong><br/>For every member of the Organization, Nation comes before anything else</p>
                            </div> 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4 ideology" >   
                        <div class="media" > 
                            <a class="pull-left" href="#">
                                <span class="fa fa-balance-scale ideology-icon"></span>
                            </a> 
                            <div class="media-body" style="padding-left: 10px; padding-top: 5px;">
                                <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 16px;"><strong>सत्यता के प्रति समर्पित</strong><br/>हम आसान काम करने के बजाय सही काम करने की प्रतिज्ञा लेते हैं</p>
                            </div> 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4 ideology" >   
                        <div class="media" > 
                            <a class="pull-left" href="#">
                                <span class="fa fa-bank ideology-icon"></span>
                            </a> 
                            <div class="media-body" style="padding-left: 10px; padding-top: 5px;">
                                <p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Uphold Banking Ethics</strong><br/>We pledge ourselves to be keen followers of Ethical Banking Culture</p>
                            </div> 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4 ideology" >   
                        <div class="media" > 
                            <a class="pull-left" href="#">
                                <span class="fa fa-twitter ideology-icon"></span>
                            </a> 
                            <div class="media-body" style="padding-left: 10px; padding-top: 5px;">
                                <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 16px;"><strong>ईमानदारी के संरक्षक</strong><br/>हम हर समय ईमानदारी की रक्षा का विश्वास दिलाते हैंं</p>
                            </div> 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4 ideology" >   
                        <div class="media" > 
                            <a class="pull-left" href="#">
                                <span class="fa fa-users ideology-icon"></span>
                            </a> 
                            <div class="media-body" style="padding-left: 10px; padding-top: 5px;">
                                <p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Happy Employees, Prosperous Bank</strong><br/>We believe that the Progress of the Bank lies in the prosperity of the Employee</p>
                            </div> 
                        </div>
                    </div>                  
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4 ideology" >   
                        <div class="media" > 
                            <a class="pull-left" href="#">
                                <span class="fa fa-handshake-o ideology-icon"></span>
                            </a> 
                            <div class="media-body" style="padding-left: 10px; padding-top: 5px;">
                                <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 16px;"><strong>सहयोगी विकास</strong><br/>हम समाज के हर भाग के साथ सहयोग करने के लिए समर्पित हैं</p>
                            </div> 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="margin-bottom: 36px;"/>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="founder col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4"> 
                    <asset:image class="pull-left" src="drDeshpandeLarge.jpg" alt="founder-bomoo" />
                    <asset:image class="pull-right" src="tikekarLarge.jpg" alt="founder-bomoo" />

                    <p class="name">Message from President and GS</p>
                    <p class="designation"></p>
                    <p class="description">Since the formation of BOMOO all dedicated members’ holds mammoth task for its growing from all corners of the country wherein our Bank has a presence. Popularity of the organisation is reflected in its increasing numerical strength as well as the faith reposed by the officers' community in it. We take this opportunity to communicate in brief about the present scenario in the banking industry..</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-8 col-md-8 col-lg-8 news"> 
                    <h3>NEWS</h3>
                    <div class="media">
                        <g:each in="${flash.news}" var="n">
                            <a class="pull-right" href=""> 
                                <img class="media-object" src="${createLink(controller:'Site', action:'getImage', params:[id: n.img.id])}"/>
                            </a> 
                            <div class="media-body">
                                <h4 class="media-heading">${n.title}</h4> 
                                <p>${n.content}</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">
                                    <g:link controller="news" style="color: white;" action="show" params="[id: n.id]"> Read </g:link>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </g:each>
                    </div>
                    <div class="read-more">
                        <g:link controller="site" action="bulletin"> Read more </g:link>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row blogs">
                <p class="heading">Recent Blogs</p>
                <div class="row">
                    <g:each in="${flash.blogs}" var="blog">
                        <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4 blog-tile">
                            <div class="blog-tile-inner" data-target="${g.createLink(controller:'Blog', action:'show', params:[id: blog.id])}" >
                                <img src="${createLink(controller:'Site', action:'getImage', params:[id: blog.img.id])}"/>
                                <p class="blog-heading"> ${ blog.title } </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </g:each>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function() {
                console.log($(window).innerHeight())
                $("#about-us-sub").hide();
            });

            $('.carousel').carousel();
            $('.btn').click(function() {
                window.location = $(this).data("location");;
            });

            $('.social-button').click(function() {
                window.location = $(this).data("location");;
            });

            $("#read-now").click(function() {
                window.location = "notice.html";
            });

            $("#read-later").click(function() {
                $(".notification-background").hide();
            });


            $(".blog-tile-inner").click(function() {
                window.location = $(this).data("target");
            });
        </script>
    </body>
</html>
